- cs.LG (Machine Learning): The paper proposes a graph-based deep learning method to learn to reason over program structures. 
- cs.SE (Software Engineering): The paper focuses on learning tasks on source code and proposes a method to represent both the syntactic and semantic structure of code. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence): The paper proposes a method to learn to reason over program structures using graph-based deep learning methods. 
- cs.PL (Programming Languages): The paper discusses the unique opportunities offered by code's known syntax and proposes a method to use graphs to represent both the syntactic and semantic structure of code. 
- cs.CL (Computation and Language): The paper mentions the transfer of natural language methods to learning tasks on source code, indicating a potential overlap with the field of natural language processing.
